{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"67a23a973e","title":"给李介侯的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c1bcee356e","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":17,"articleId":"67a23a973e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"d884f46836","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李介候（1899—1971），湖南省韶山市韶山乡韶北村人。早年毕业于湖南机械专门学校。当时在长沙经商。后在北京中国进口公司机械科、外贸部进出口机械总公司工作。"},{"id":"96d098e408","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"耿侯，即李耿侯（1889-1928），李介侯的胞兄。1925年加入中国共产党，曾任湖南湘潭（韶山）特别区农民协会执行委员、中共湘潭（韶山）特别区委组织委员、韶山农民自卫军负责人。1928年在湘南晒性。"},{"id":"60423eef60","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指李介候的父亲李激清（1874-1957），乡村教师。新中国成立后，曾任湖南省文物管理委员会委员、湖南省文史研究馆馆员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4bd9bf9b74","type":"title","text":"给李介侯的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e"},{"id":"d884f46836","type":"paragraph","text":"介侯先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e"},{"id":"96d098e408","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书敬悉，深感厚意。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e"},{"id":"60423eef60","type":"paragraph","text":"耿侯兄自一九二八年在湘赣边界之宁冈县见过一面，随即率队返湘南以后，未再见过。传闻狗难，似属可信，时地则无从查问了。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e"},{"id":"ebd2fcb0cd","type":"paragraph","text":"尊翁健存，可为庆贺，尚祈转致问候之意。率复，顺祝健进！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e"},{"id":"968226267a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e"},{"id":"5b19c61f77","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年十一月十七日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e"}],"page":{"id":"7d501db544","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"67a23a973e","start":521,"end":521}}}},"__N_SSG":true}